The Contender;;73;;76;;R;;When the sitting Vice President dies, Senator Laine Hanson is chosen by the President to be the first woman to hold the office. The selection meets with opposition from members of both parties, in particular a powerful political adversary who will seemingly stop at nothing to discredit her. Her confirmation hearings set off a firestorm of controversy as shocking secrets from Hanson's past are revealed, threatening her personal life as well as her political future.;;Mystery & thriller;;Rod Lurie;;2000;;Joan Allen,Gary Oldman,Jeff Bridges,Sam Elliott,Christian Slater,William Petersen,Philip Baker Hall,Saul Rubinek;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1100998-contender